title: (Tues Full) Someone On The Show Got a New Job and Lunchbox Loses His Mind + Can Amy Name the Gen Z Pop Artist? + When Bobby Is Doing More Comedy Shows This Summer!
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Someone On The Show Got a New Job and Lunchbox Loses His Mind + Can Amy Name the Gen Z Pop Artist? + When Bobby Is Doing More Comedy Shows This Summer!
description:
Someone on the show reveals a new job opportunity and Lunchbox loses his mind. Bobby plays Amy a song from a Gen Z pop artist…if she can identify the artist, she will win a prize for the caller! Bobby gives you the top 5 life hacks recommended if you find yourself in a situation where you don’t have toilet paper. Bobby makes an informal announcement about when his next round of comedy shows are happening in Nashville.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
